{"tid":800511,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"PR vs In-house MKT","createTime":"2018-08-31T02:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T14:57:03.000Z","uid":82167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b028265bf28dd172201650558f9718ad1ece2504","tid":800511,"uid":82167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:44:36.000Z","msg":"岩岩轉左份in-house mkt<br />\n但做左兩個幾月感覺唔適合<br />\n做既野唔係想像中既mkt野<br />\n好多跟order, 貨期既野 有啲係license野 <br />\n行業唔係好廣 平日做既野好似都係成日對住excel 自己唔太鐘意<br />\n但勝在時間穩定 唔多ot<br />\n人工15k 但返呢份工都返得唔太開心  <br />\n<br />\n而最近都忍唔住搵工<br />\n有份consultants 公司既比左Offer我<br />\n而呢間公司有做政府機構, 私人機構既PR<br />\n老闆都幾勁 （行內）<br />\n而比起數字 自己都比較鐘意文字工作<br />\n但人工得14 佢話半年出一次performance bonus <br />\n預左做PR會辛苦好多 同埋ot好勁 星期六日都可能要返<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得我應該點揀？自己最想就係將來競爭力好啲，可以叫價高啲<br />\n<br />\n利申：17年非三大畢業<br />\n<br />\n謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5664309e0019564a464fd6b800af5bc20153760","tid":800511,"uid":2270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T03:38:39.000Z","msg":"咁多人對PR, Marketing 有幻想, 你做完都知係打雜工一份，轉field 好過la。"},{"pid":"ac2b08cf9420344b02088eaf4b4ee54cd351da6b","tid":800511,"uid":162053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:44:05.000Z","msg":"pr boune有都分好少、日日做既野都係差唔多 唔好expect成日見客對人 都係office打雜打下文件<br />\n<br />\nps: 做過pr intern"},{"pid":"e82c0eb4f5d62b26da2e58bd34f4acb82487ddd5","tid":800511,"uid":36674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:57:03.000Z","msg":"Title係咩？真係pr?"}]}